<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Floor Level</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/custom/AW1P1FloorStyles.css">
</head>
<body>

    <div class="grid-container">
        <div class="grid-item" onclick="openModal(1)">
            <div class="floor">Floor 1</div>
            <div class="method">Methods</div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-item" onclick="openModal(2)">
            <div class="floor">Floor 2</div>
            <div class="method">Calling a Method</div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-item" onclick="openModal(3)">
            <div class="floor">Floor 3</div>
            <div class="method">Parameters and Arguments</div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-item" onclick="openModal(4)">
            <div class="floor">Floor 4</div>
            <div class="method">Return Values</div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-item" onclick="openModal(5)">
            <div class="floor">Floor 5</div>
            <div class="method">Condition Statements</div>
        </div>
        <div id="backButton">Back to Part Selection</div>
    </div>

    <div id="modal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <h2>Instructions</h2>
            <h4 id="floorTitle"></h4>
            <ol>
                <li><b>Question Types:</b> There are 4 types (3-Identifications, 3-Multiple Choices, 4-What's the Output, 4-Complete the Code) with different point values (2, 2, 3, and 4 points each total of 40).</li>
                <li><b>Time Limits:</b> Finish all questions within 10 Minutes.</li>
                <li><b>Lives:</b> You get 3 tries per question. Lose all 3 tries, lose 1 point.</li>
                <li><b>Hints:</b> Get 3 hints per question. 1st hint is free, 2nd & 3rd cost 100 silver coins.</li>
                <li><b>Rewards:</b> Earn 100 silver coins for each correct answer and 100 gold coins for finishing this floor.</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="modal-buttons">
                <button id="goButton" class="modal-button go">Go</button>
                <button id="closeButton" class="modal-button back">Back</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="~/js/custom/AW1P1FloorScript.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
